The Windows Installer version configures {{FISHEYE_INST}} as a Windows environment variable, however that variable is *not used at all*.

If someone wants to change the {{FISHEYE_INST}} location, these are the steps:

# Stop the FishEye/Crucible instance;
# Go to {{Windows Start Menu > All Programs > FishEye > Configure FishEye}}
# In the {{Atlassian FeCru Properties}} window, go to {{Java}} tab;
# Locate and update the {{-Dfisheye.inst}} parameter in the {{Java Options}} list.
# Close the {{Atlassian FeCru Properties}} window;
# Start the FishEye/Crucible service.

When that setting is updated, the Windows environment variable should be updated as well.

